data.description:
Welcome Home! This beautiful and updated 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in the desired Woodbridge Station is awaiting its next owners. This home boasts mature trees, has great curb appeal and a welcoming front garden space. Inside the front door you will be greeted by a large and sunny dining room. The nearby designer kitchen features top of the line appliances including an oversized commercial refrigerator, cooktop with range hood, built in microwave, oven and warming drawer, dishwasher and extra bar seating perfect for gatherings. The oversized island emphasizes open concept living with two separate seating areas and ample pantry storage. 
Upstairs you will find two generously sized bedrooms that border a full bathroom. Down the stairs and off the kitchen is a large garden level living room perfect for relaxing or watching your favorite channels. The entertainment built-ins allow for added media storage. This oversized space has also been utilized for home office purposes. The nearby great full bathroom with shower has been nicely remodeled and offers easy access off the living room. Downstairs, the basement features a large laundry room with extra storage. The basement primary suite has its own private oasis with great walk-in closet. Outside, the backyard has a spacious utility shed perfect for all of your storage needs. This nice lot is a great place to catch sunshine and soak up the outdoors. The deck is a wonderful space to gather and enjoy the serene backyard. This home falls within Adams 12 5 star school district and offers close proximity to grocery, dining, shopping, parks and the local library. Also, it has a very low HOA and taxes! This charming home won't last long!
